{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"1329","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":null,"news_on_top":"1","news_title":"日本逾8成5企業替員工加薪 平均金額逾千元","news_summary":null,"image_path":null,"news_des":"","news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>時間：2022-11-23 13:04 新聞引據：中央社 撰稿編輯：新聞編輯</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC.jpg' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;' /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>日本政府厚生勞動省調查顯示，今年有約85.7%的日本企業已經或將要替員工加薪。示意圖。(圖：中央社)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr style='box-sizing: content-box; border-radius: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 20px 0px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent); color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;' />\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>日本政府厚生勞動省調查顯示，今年有約85.7%的日本企業已經或將要替員工加薪，較去年調查成長5個百分點，平均加薪金額約為5534日圓（約新台幣1220元），加薪幅度約1.9%。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>日本放送協會（NHK）報導，厚生勞動省每年針對員工人數超過百人的企業例行性調查加薪狀況，今年共獲2020家企業答覆。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>調查顯示，今年共有約85.7%的日本企業已經或將要替員工加薪，較去年成長5個百分點。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>過去受到COVID-19疫情影響，替員工加薪的日本企業比率已連續兩年低於前一年，今年是3年來首度較前一年增加。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>厚生勞動省表示，雖然加薪幅度還無法回到COVID-19疫情前水準，但業績回復的企業普遍都有調薪，也可以看到因物價上漲的薪資調漲。隨著企業業績持續回復，研判也將為明年調薪帶來正面影響。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'>資料來源:&nbsp;</span><a href='https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2151423' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 158, 184); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px !important;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2151423</span></a></span></p>\r\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2022-11-29","clk_count":"50"}},"__N_SSG":true}